{"tid":1706041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"PolyU係咪有病？10點43分先宣布全日停課？有無人識得反抗下 打去鬧教務處？校長呢？","createTime":"2019-11-11T03:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T03:55:54.000Z","uid":270106,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94e2a2035596713c1b8059ede0e9b6390ecd6d3f","tid":1706041,"uid":270106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">朝早到宜家發生咁多事 港大中大理大三間TG放題 就係你poly停課半日？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人命同考試比 睇黎呢個藍到發紫紅到變黨員嘅校長覺得後者緊要好多</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n認住佢啦 <br />\n滕錦光<br />\n之前拒絕同畢業禮戴口罩學生握手<br />\n中國科技界出名吖嘛<br />\n翻大陸啦<br />\n今日又由得poly比popo比tg轟炸<br />\n都繼續要學生考試翻學<br />\n<br />\n唔係淨系翻唔翻學呢個位緊要<br />\n係唔重視人命<br />\n<br />\n以後得啦<br />\n繼續扮無野啦呢間學校可以<br />\n停課就怪學生怪暴徒啦<br />\n屌<br />\n仲話：「希望高等教育積極爭取落大灣區」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAN4Q5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAN4Q5D.jpg&h=02f32193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算你係咪poly仔女 <br />\n都應該反抗<br />\npoly嘅仔女<br />\n你地接受緊高等教育架各位<br />\n真心<br />\n今日poly有8點幾考試<br />\n都唔話取消<br />\n大佬 有無理會過學生啊 係咪咁政治冷感住象牙塔咁開心啊<br />\n<br />\n好想喊<br />\n呢間紅磚建築坐落於平衡時空<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔講喇 嬲到喊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n有人去中環有無手足去理大"},{"pid":"3f37723128f42f7cbc7fefad029c59f10debcbd7","tid":1706041,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港<br />\n奴隸之都</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ae1bd8ce12e4385f264ca8a31c48ebb8f40720c","tid":1706041,"uid":270106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"十點半後先話全日停課<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">論香港人的奴性</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span st